Why isn't `fp.assign` mutating `a`? Since there's no documentation for the `lodash/fp` functions except for the FP guide and the FP guide doesn't point out this difference in behaviour (or does it?), I expect both `_.assign` and `fp.assign` to behave the same. What am I missing?
